Changelog for minidns
=====================

0.4 (unreleased)
----------------

- Allow domain list to be locked down using the configuration file
- Use nameservers listed in /etc/resolv.conf if they are not localhost, otherwise default to Google's

0.3 (2013-09-11)
----------------

- Fix bug in get_record


0.2 (2013-09-11)
----------------

- Updated response on PUT to domain from 405 to 200 if it already exists


0.1 (2013-09-11)
----------------

- Original release.

